Package: providenceri.gov
Title: Providence RI Open Data (Socrata SODA) Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the City of Providence Open Data Socrata
    SODA API at data.providenceri.gov. Covers dataset listing, search, SoQL
    queries, and named functions for police arrests, case logs, expenditures,
    property tax, budgets, permits, schools, trees, food trucks, pensions, and
    more. Includes LLM context injection via pvd_context().
